    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every aspect of the car has been meticulously preserved, from the flawless original paint and pristine interior to the high-performance engine that runs perfectly. It has been kept in a climate-controlled environment, includes a full service history with no expense spared, and features all original equipment in working order. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning driver to own a top-tier example of this model that requires absolutely nothing but a new owner.",
      "price": 48500.0,
